column4: A tall man wearing a dark velvet suit and a fine silver watch.
He is a glowering man with weathered features. Were he not wearing a fine suit one may think him to be ill equipeed and poorly resourced. But... He is wearing the suit.
A lanky man with odd features–Perhaps unpleasant features at that. His eyes are accusative and supicious...
Five feet tall is a little elss than average. Yet this man seems to carry himself with some certainty about him...
Arthur is a fellow agent. His trenchcoat is ragged and disheveled–though you know he's only deceiving by appearance.
